    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "yShzV/KSLwy6peR9X5gc/jQ6A7/QojYDiGFjDXoDrb8=",
    "originContent": "This is a self-hosted docker-compose configuration for [SimpleLogin](https://simplelogin.io).",
    "translatedContent": "これは [SimpleLogin](https://simplelogin.io) 用のセルフホスト型 docker-compose 構成です。"
